text: Flavia Vigna (born 7 December 1990) is a Brazilian water polo player. She was part of the Brazilian women's water polo team at the 2009 World Aquatics Championships, and 2013 World Aquatics Championships in Barcelona, Spain, where they finished 14th. == References == == Other websites == * https://thepioneeronline.com/23785/sports/csueb-womens-water-polo-falls-to- brazil/ * https://hawaiiathletics.com/news/2015/3/29/WWP_0329154958.aspx Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Brazilian water polo players
